Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today’s news is about Gao Kao. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays Chinese students have a lot of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piles of homework, never-ending weekend classes, competitive exams, and no doubt the gaokao leads to enormous pressure for Chinese students to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suggest to relieve all of that stress?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I personally like drawing, and walking in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are also other ways to relieve stress. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year, Chinese students are again getting creative with their stress relief methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already heard from the news how Chinese students are taking creative graduation photos. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are students being creative with stress relief? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my favorite way is balloon-stomping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Students in Hefei, Anhui stomped balloons before taking the gaokao. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The excitement surely made them forget about the difficulty of the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a great way! Were they allowed to stomp the balloons at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. As a matter of fact, most of these stress-relief methods require the school’s support. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, students sitting the gaokao at a school in Hengshui, Hebei all received ten yuan before taking each test. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s very generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also other ways, such as massages at school, and student-teacher activities on the sports field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all sounds like a lot of fun!